title: Brave Mom Exposes Vaccine Corruption To WA Board of Health
description:
Bernadette Pajer of Informed Choice Washington - https://www.informedchoicewa.org - gave the WA Board of Health a lashing for its complicity in the vaccine industry's plan to force vaccinate every man, woman and child on this planet. This is a MUST WATCH VIDEO!!! "Michelle Roberts and every single immunization program head in every single state has a mission to remove our human right to medical choice, to silence the very real risks and limitations of vaccines, and they are doing so with the full support, collaboration and education of Pfizer and Merck and Glaxo Smith Kline and [others] who were all there at the conference in June. THIS MUST STOP." SHARE! This is how we do it!
